   Kassa, Alemayehu; Konrad, Heino; Geburek, Thomas, Austrian Res Ctr Forests BFW, Dept Forest Genet, Seckendorff Gudent Weg 8, A-1131 Vienna, Austria.
   Kassa, Alemayehu, Gondar Agr Res Ctr, Gondar 1337, Ethiopia.},
