   Hufford, Kristina M.; Hamrick, J. L., Univ Georgia, Dept Plant Biol, Athens, GA 30602 USA.
   Rathbun, Stephen L., Univ Georgia, Dept Hlth Adm Biostat \& Epidemiol, Athens, GA 30602 USA.},
